               unlawfully uttering a counterfeit shilling, knowing it to be false and counterfeit, and at the same time having one other counterfeit shilling in his possession
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18181028-142-victim973" type="victimName">
                  THOMAS 
                  BRUCE
               <interp inst="t18181028-142-victim973" type="surname" value="BRUCE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18181028-142-victim973" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
